            "Average gradient $=\\dfrac{7-3}{2-0}=2$"
          ],
          "answer": "$2$"
        },
        {
          "q": "Calculate the vertical distance between $f$ and $g$ at $x=3$.",
          "marks": 2,
          "solution": [
            "$f(3)=12$, $g(3)=9$",
            "Vertical distance $=12-9=3$"
          ],
          "answer": "$3$ units"
        },
        {
          "q": "Determine the $x$-values where $f$ and $g$ intersect.",
          "marks": 2,
          "solution": [
            "$x^2+3=2x+3$",
            "$x^2-2x=0\\Rightarrow x(x-2)=0$",
            "$x=0$ or $x=2$"
          ],
          "answer": "$x=0$ or $x=2$"
        }
      ]
    },
